title: Immigration Attitude
text: What is the expected immigration attitude of someone who is liberal and starts with an attitude of 6? See Chapter 6 for details.

title: Immigration Attitude
text:
Model
\[y_i = \beta_0  + \beta_1 x_{1,i} + \beta_2 x_{2,i}\] with \(y = att\_end\), \(x_1 = att\_start\), and \(x_2 = liberal\).
